      "reference_id": "3edf8aec-a9ef-499c-888c-ef00c42296dc",
      "text": "Thus, the authors want to use the fact that students create causal diagrams for studying to create automatic assessments on that causal diagram. This is a specific case of learning where students use causal relation diagrams to consolidate their knowledge.",
